import React from 'react'
import { Card, TextField, Typography, Container } from '@material-ui/core'

export const LogInView = () => {
    
    return(
        <Container>
            <Card>
                <Typography>Nickname</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
                
                <Typography>Email</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
                
                <Typography>Password</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
            </Card>
            <Card>
                <Typography>Nickname</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
                
                <Typography>Email</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
                
                <Typography>Password</Typography>
                <TextField></TextField>
            </Card>
        </Container>
    )
}
